## 9. HTTP Requests (REST Client / Postman)
```http
### Generate Invoice
POST http://localhost:3000/invoices/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "clientId": "uuid-here",
  "billingPeriodStart": "2024-12-01",
  "billingPeriodEnd": "2024-12-31",
  "invoiceDate": "2024-12-14",
  "notes": "Monthly garbage collection"
}

### Get Invoice by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/invoices/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List All Invoices
GET http://localhost:3000/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List Invoices with Filters
GET http://localhost:3000/invoices?clientId={{clientId}}&status=PENDING&fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Invoices by Client
GET http://localhost:3000/invoices/client/{{clientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Invoice Status
PATCH http://localhost:3000/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "OVERDUE"
}
```

